{"article_id":"CqApZSG6QfqfiJbc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump took to Twitter early Friday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"issuing yet another stark warning to North Korea","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that the United States ' military was \" locked and loaded , \"","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and urged the rogue regime ' s dictator to \" find another path . \"","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" Military solutions are now fully in place , locked and loaded ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"should North Korea act unwisely .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Hopefully Kim Jong Un will find another path ! \"","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"the president tweeted Friday morning , amid escalating tensions this week .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Trump ' s tweet comes after days of tough rhetoric toward the regime ,","depth":3},{"id":9,"text":"which has made several threats to the United States amid a new United Nations sanctions package","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"that was passed unanimously last week .","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"Earlier this week , Trump reacted to reports","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that North Korea had produced a compact nuclear warhead","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"and warned the country","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"they \" will be met with fire and fury \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"if they carry out an attack .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Hours later , state media in North Korea reported","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that its leaders were seriously considering a plan","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"to fire missiles at Guam .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"\" Let ' s see what he does with Guam .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"He does something in Guam ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"it will be an event","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"the likes of which nobody has seen before","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"-what will happen in North Korea , \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said Thursday , at his property in Bedminster , N.J. , in response to Kim Jong Un ' s threats","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to attack the U.S. territory .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" It ' s not a dare ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"it ' s a statement . \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Trump added :","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" He has disrespected our country greatly .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"He has said things","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that are horrific .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"And with me , he ' s not getting away with it .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"It ' s a whole new ball game . \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"The president has faced some criticism in Washington for the tone of his rhetoric against Pyongyang ,","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"with lawmakers warning","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he could needlessly escalate the standoff .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"But Trump maintained Thursday","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"his words might not have been `` tough enough . ''","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"The warnings from Trump come","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"as China","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"- North Korea ' s primary ally -","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"issued a veiled warning to the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"China ' s government , via state media , said","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"it would remain neutral","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"if North Korea attacks the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"but would defend its neighbor","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"if the U.S. were to strike first against Kim Jong Un .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Meanwhile , other Asia-Pacific countries ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"including Japan and Australia ,","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"have come out in support of the United States in the event of a North Korean nuclear attack .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":101,"left":61,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":58,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":54,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren